<author>hrmạs smyr, hrmạs smyr</author>
<title>bsmʿ ạlạ̉dẖn</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (bsmʿ ạlạ̉dẖn qd smʿt ʿnk .. wạlận qd rạ̉tk ʿyny)2
 1- (wjdt ḥbyby fạ̉mskth .. wạ̹ly̱ kẖbạỷy qd ạ̉dkẖlth)2
 kyf ạ̉ʿwd wạ̉trkh
 2- (mn dẖạ ygẖnyny ʿn ạ̹ny ạ̉rạk .. mạdẖạ ysẖfyny gẖyr rḍạk)2
 mạdẖạ ykfyny ʿn ḥbk swạk
 3- (zạdny jwʿy ạ̹lyk ạ̹sẖtyạq .. ẓmận qlby ạ̹ly̱ lqạk)2
 lytny ạ̉sẖbʿ mn rw̉yạk
 4- (yḥlw lnfsy ạ̹lyk ạ̹qtrạby .. fyṣyr tbr ạlqlb kạltrạb)2
 ḥytẖ lạ yfṣlnạ ạ̹y ḥjạb</lyrics>
</song>